name: Smithsonian'sNationalZooCalendar
0:
”Alexa, open national zoo calendar”
”Ask national zoo calendar to get me events for today”
”What events are happening on August 1st”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: national zoo calendar
des: National Zoo calendar gives you the complete information about the events happening on "The National Zoological Park", commonly known as the National Zoo, one of the oldest zoos located at Rock Creek Park in Northwest Washington, D.C., the United States.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
